Clare Holman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clare_Holman 0 Clare Margaret Holman (born 12 January 1964) is an English actress. She portrayed forensic pathologist Dr. Laura Hobson in the television series Inspector Morse and Lewis from 1995 to 2015. Clare_Margaret_Holman ( born 12_January_1964 ) is an_English_actress .
